Revision history for Class-Lego-Constructor.

0.004    ????
        - Exporter::Lite is no longer a prerequisite
        - defer/lazy are not exported anymore
          (which hides the dependency on Scalar::Defer)
        - new mk_constructor1
        - usage pattern of mk_constructor0 changed
          (not backwards compatible)

0.003    Mon Feb 18 2008
        - dist renamed from Class-Constructor-Factory to
          Class-Lego-Constructor

0.002    Tue Jan  2 2008
        - dependency upgraded to Scalar::Defer 0.13
        - mk_constructor0 is a class method and
          should not be exported

0.001    Wed Dec 27 2007
        - first CPAN release
        - ugly, undocumented, but working
